INSTALLATION
============
chdir to the root directory (containing this README), and type the commands:

$ cmake spike/
$ make 

RUN
===
Simply type:
$ ./HMM


DEPENDENCIES
============
- Boost c++ libraries (get from boost.org site)
- cmake tool set

GOOD LUCK!